{"id": 1614, "genre": 1001, "title": "来，谈谈你没谈恋爱的原因是什么？", "description": "是激情的沦丧还是对自由的不舍得。（题图：Canon PowerShot Sx400 Is）", "record_count": 9577, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170406144824e6hlM0OQLoZ4qYvf.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-12T03:00:06Z", "options": [{"id": 188928, "content": "不喜欢固定关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 149, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 190976, "content": "恋爱中的自己总是失去自我，太过感性，也太能作，所以不敢再谈", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981846}, {"id": 191232, "content": "交友障碍", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620962}, {"id": 191488, "content": "我还早着呢，不玩早恋?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991400}, {"id": 191744, "content": "想得太多，行动太少。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003109}, {"id": 193024, "content": "总觉得不会长久，那些男生看重外貌，觉得自己不够好，要花很多时间，感觉不自在，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006244}, {"id": 193536, "content": "习惯了一个人，不想让自己走出7舒适区", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1000533}, {"id": 201473, "content": "没有符合要求的:)高中选择太少了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025616}, {"id": 190977, "content": "我自己就是个有趣的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323807}, {"id": 191489, "content": "这不是你单身的理由?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982140}, {"id": 191745, "content": "不想恋爱 只想发财", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 54926}, {"id": 192001, "content": "与别人分享我们古稀后的步履蹒跚\n虐死单身狗", "image": "img/option/option/20170413121814U93M2ad60QREWwXG", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003467}, {"id": 192257, "content": "没人主动追求。?扎心了，老铁", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003941}, {"id": 190978, "content": "接触不到异性啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 985530}, {"id": 191234, "content": "两个有趣的灵魂相遇太难", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929487}, {"id": 191490, "content": "都是借口，不是穷就是丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671023}, {"id": 191746, "content": "少了很多认真去谈恋爱的心！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334789}, {"id": 192770, "content": "不甘心啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863495}, {"id": 191235, "content": "嗯", "image": "img/option/option/20170412155558irloB8hcXWtNn9Cx.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 86689}, {"id": 191491, "content": "浪费感情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170504}, {"id": 191747, "content": "自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981629}, {"id": 192003, "content": "总觉得合适的没出现，然后就没有然后了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988514}, {"id": 190980, "content": "因为她不喜欢我", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206864}, {"id": 191236, "content": "价值观没有相似的", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 778133}, {"id": 191748, "content": "想对别人好但是有心无力却又希望别人对自己好到不行，是个挑剔五银猫", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003117}, {"id": 190981, "content": "喜欢人可能需要一分钟，但是忘掉可能需要一辈子", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002359}, {"id": 191749, "content": "没有表白的勇气", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 571647}, {"id": 190982, "content": "没有谈的来的，害怕受伤", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993552}, {"id": 191238, "content": "现在的恋爱都以结婚为前提，这对不向往婚姻的人来说并不是件好事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002570}, {"id": 191494, "content": "一个人真的好开心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002838}, {"id": 191750, "content": "因为爱一个人太慢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786933}, {"id": 192518, "content": "没有喜欢的女生 虽然有时候会憧憬恋爱但是一个人真的很好 而且接触的女生也比较少 再加上自己比较低调 没有很想恋爱的冲动 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004763}, {"id": 192774, "content": "自己的情绪太容易被他影响", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981647}, {"id": 194310, "content": "完全没有认识女孩的机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 861883}, {"id": 191239, "content": "我不知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002574}, {"id": 191495, "content": "没成为理想的自己，没遇到理想的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955609}, {"id": 191751, "content": "不知道为什么，对恋爱感觉既渴望又拒绝", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403578}, {"id": 194055, "content": "我也不知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008485}, {"id": 190984, "content": "胖", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002364}, {"id": 191240, "content": "不够勇敢和自信", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906067}, {"id": 191496, "content": "不愿意花钱\n先自私完再说", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960897}, {"id": 193032, "content": "还没有遇到真正动心的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1005715}, {"id": 199177, "content": "不想祸害别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958052}, {"id": 190985, "content": "说和水瓶谈恋爱，就和水瓶谈恋爱...我大水瓶不是这么好追的=_=", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794210}, {"id": 191241, "content": "各种阴差阳错之后，好像就失去了喜欢上一个人的能力了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 550670}, {"id": 191497, "content": "不会，不信，不喜欢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935957}, {"id": 191753, "content": "双方都怕流言蜚语", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780745}, {"id": 192009, "content": "没有目标", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003511}, {"id": 193289, "content": "等我再努力一些，等我变得优秀..", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001239}, {"id": 190986, "content": "喜欢人的，不喜欢我。没有喜欢我的人。其他的，不愿意将就，不想要辜负", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960354}]}